'''Boaboo fungus''' was grown on [[Sullust/Legends|Sullust]]. The fungus was grown in caverns, and had many different breeds. [[Sullustan/Legends|Sullustans]] such as [[Bungo Bung]]'s father cultivated farms of the fungus. The fungus was then mashed into [[Boaboo juice]] and sold to the general populace. Boaboo fungus was very moist, and was tended mainly by [[Droid/Legends|droids]].

